# Example system architecture diagram
graph TB
    A[Client App] -->|HTTPS| B[Load Balancer]
    B --> C[Web Server 1]
    B --> D[Web Server 2]
    C --> E[Database]
    D --> E[Database]
    E --> F[Backup Storage]
    
    subgraph "Security Zone"
